KhPvpxzdzJZ7a8BMEK6FFzJKAWNFxECHZj1pLwMXqLkot12FafCRIV5ht9DgteK4CAW0G-mof3x7ZdRGiMkh4CnkHz4h34F4WJOZX4s0bTjPSud_pKaqU8SB0lRJcohUdGtqKA-rLxF3Sylk5RzCtMMbpwEY95KwXiF8wvxf3sASGoCfHlicLQevz-pCIIdalrAF5K4qbpgsli9iOEgynu1Zg5uG1ONEafMHe4MKvDBGHlOubRIP4WIjMQwc-xySju1SJW6fKvueKdsuFkQZ19-zrSEzIIBpZTajsHs4UJe4G0m3YtbcMV-oRkzTyGKmR8Xm-URnhrw6ltungxM8OO6TcjraHB88D8wvlssebmF2EAhREmlyGEilCbh5rxOwYetaVOJAxg8LfNC9F2jq8YCa6nsHkoxAzbLUVyOMBj9Dd31BCFLP4SiN4Z7_RUODiSUQaK_0lXsN/4sTBIBiJ8yE9UuQpk01Olq5dv9DYaXy8/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="最高法院刚刚废除了投票权法"&gt;最高法院最近推动的&lt;/a&gt;十年中期的激进选区重新划分，是他陷入僵局、备受争议的选民身份立法，该立法将在全国范围内要求美国人出示带有照片的身份证明并出示美国公民身份证明才能投票。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;周三，特朗普找到了一个新的理由要求国会通过该法案， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/lr7caR3zX2YBEZYX0TOlNhW-RexqBwDoEwl5eLEU9SZkA58Hp9nQ49itr49mMyx2hgn2H7FW37k0KXfLffp9yqTobNdXY7tYiSBjJrjhlONA5GXJ7sA6nHiYiNAod6soKWMoENBAvgaTh8V2_JeNQioeuXrxaFNQx3EHirPNadJr1J2KJAY9H1GmnxI0VI7a-aw4W0KdjEsxyRxKz28E4wjc-MdPeOtaCrSm7cKR3Xb601eu2q4Fikvqwsv4dLyAwqLJccSEKhw-EPLmnsBKl7CSvhODnVNCNbhRId4-ntMJeS0QncFbaqP8o1EnbIHf0mg65vdKeEu1fC3a_bW5RHpHX29q-njYXojAvz4iaTATL3-Gh1WV_VrbMW6chTds-u9bVG5YnRh3aoRDqDcSh0WhX__LtQMlKN-esnX_c66DeMn9TIPT0QeVjpfa5FTuOtBQoiWz5hUQOCnAV4R735htlh32cejA3n47-XtSIx2PGmgD4RZwzItP_1E_uX4pyXJEI7qDBxhr1WGmGoMK/Sg0kNYDLqbONgVkiqt_GJi-P192SaTjF/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="总统废除住房法案签署后，特朗普与共和党发生冲突"&gt;拒绝签署一项罕见的两党住房法案，&lt;/a&gt;除非参议院共和党人推动通过他的法律。特朗普以有关选民欺诈的虚假指控为其辩护，尽管该措施几乎不存在，但批评人士认为，这是共和党几乎不加掩饰的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/RZosox56pYlSNEybFtK7KySe25-yuMvtN248M7d47BIc4wlGoT-BhuiiGC2yjCvK_3KcSHI-scEiCkUrPdljCh3kW0PVrK9rktFhqo0aGX5sXocIiXur4k2s4A7O4LUh005AEBRZ6gcTpmp5CF6nrOG2lcpEyNqudzECSr_0eG_FDnYubeyIYyqhkH7hADKFU59WQFM9AAjbl-cIpLswaaq--H3vR3ihU7Ml_k_x2XcShS0mEgCaOWQxi0seGW5nXw6vCX7SzrA9Npv34DuoHhCiqjqbqNniuT1Q1onakK5zjbxqIsLjyueH0roBp7HOHqiq